<item>
            <title>[WICKET-6570] Unable to read cookies containing &apos;.&apos; characters in names when using CookieUtils </title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/WICKET-6570</link>
                <project id="12310561" key="WICKET">Wicket</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;We are using CookieUtils for reading some 3rd party cookies from the request. This cookies however contains &apos;.&apos; characters (in their names) and CookieUtils replaces all &apos;.&apos; with &apos;..&apos; So those cookies are not readable anymore.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;org.apache.wicket.util.cookies.CookieUtils#getSaveKey(String key) :&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;// cookie names cannot contain &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;:&apos;&lt;/span&gt;,
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;// we replace &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;:&apos;&lt;/span&gt; with &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;.&apos;&lt;/span&gt; but first we have to encode &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;.&apos;&lt;/span&gt; as &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;..&apos;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;key = Strings.replaceAll(key, &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;.&quot;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;..&quot;&lt;/span&gt;).toString();
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Why is &apos;.&apos; replaced with &apos;..&apos;? Is &apos;.&apos; in a cookie name forbidden character?&lt;/p&gt;</description>
