                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="16554457" author="florianlacreuse" created="Tue, 24 Jul 2018 16:09:33 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;FWIW, it&apos;s related to issue &lt;del&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/WICKET-1834&quot; title=&quot;Invalid Cookie Names for persistence used according to RFC (doesn&amp;#39;t work in tomcat 6.x)&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;WICKET-1834&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;WICKET-1834&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/del&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16627157" author="svenmeier" created="Tue, 25 Sep 2018 11:00:31 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;When a component&apos;s model is saved into / loaded from a cookie, CookieUtils escapes the component path separator &apos;:&apos; with &apos;.&apos;.&lt;br/&gt;
To prevent name clashes with dots in other component&apos;s paths these are encoded with &apos;..&apos; first.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;For now you can override CookieUtils#getSaveKey(String) to return the key without any escaping.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;For Wicket 9 we will change CookieUtils to do its escaping only for #save(FormComponent) and #load(FormComponent) and leave cookie names untouched otherwise.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16627162" author="jan-krakora" created="Tue, 25 Sep 2018 11:04:54 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;OK, thank you for explanation. I will do that.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16627192" author="jira-bot" created="Tue, 25 Sep 2018 11:37:53 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Commit 584b7f6a20aa1ac2aaa3751c3e45283f481d1bcf in wicket&apos;s branch refs/heads/master from &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=svenmeier&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;svenmeier&quot;&gt;svenmeier&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
[ &lt;a href=&quot;https://git-wip-us.apache.org/repos/asf?p=wicket.git;h=584b7f6&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://git-wip-us.apache.org/repos/asf?p=wicket.git;h=584b7f6&lt;/a&gt; ]&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/WICKET-6570&quot; title=&quot;Unable to read cookies containing &amp;#39;.&amp;#39; characters in names when using CookieUtils &quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;WICKET-6570&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;WICKET-6570&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; escape component cookies only&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16627194" author="svenmeier" created="Tue, 25 Sep 2018 11:39:17 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Cookie name is escaped only when loaded or saved for a component.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
